package:graphql
class:CategoriesSpec
scenario:retrieving information about all categories

request:
```graphql
    query findAllCategories {
        categories {
            id
            name
        }
    }
```

response:
{
	"data": {
		"categories": [
			[2]{
				"id": <id>,
				"name": <name>
			}
		]
	}
}

examples:

| should                    | id  | name         |
| ------------------------- | --- | ------------ |
| "retrieve all categories" | 1   | "RAM memory" |
| *                         | 2   | "SSD disk"   |
